接口 KeyComparable<T extends MultiBucketsAggregation.Bucket & KeyComparable<T>>

  • 类型参数:
    T - MultiBucketsAggregation.Bucket of the same type that also implements KeyComparable.
    所有已知实现类:
    InternalDateHistogram.Bucket, InternalHistogram.Bucket, InternalTerms.Bucket, LongTerms.Bucket, StringTerms.Bucket, UnmappedTerms.Bucket

    public interface KeyComparable<T extends MultiBucketsAggregation.Bucket & KeyComparable<T>>
    Defines behavior for comparing bucket keys to imposes a total ordering of buckets of the same type.
    另请参阅:
    BucketOrder.key(boolean)

      • compareKey

        int compareKey(T other)
        Compare this MultiBucketsAggregation.Buckets key with another bucket.
        参数:
        other - the bucket that contains the key to compare to.
        返回:
        a negative integer, zero, or a positive integer as this buckets key is less than, equal to, or greater than the other buckets key.
        另请参阅:
        Comparable.compareTo(Object)
